<sections> 
  <clause id="_management_oversight_of_information_security" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Management oversight of information security</title><clause id="_general" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>General</title>   
  <requirement id="_d648cafb-db39-4d35-b06c-d87cd6d70248"><label>/ss/584/2015/general/632</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><description><p id="_0ec60a0b-214e-4053-b92c-d24d9a307801">The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors shall be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures.</p>    
</description><specification exclude="true">     
  <p id="_56b35fb2-db5d-4b0f-8f70-036024cf1551">be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures</p>     
</specification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_1_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 1 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_a226e231-f190-4fea-89c9-de61d8dc3786"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/1</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><specification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_7021c8e4-9a73-44f1-8c7f-9455ade45deb" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_ca5fb190-4ef6-4bf6-ad8f-d1d0a429e8d3">Managing information security risks related to people, process, technology and governance.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_b4575d76-6835-4d92-86ef-073d316e91ec">Oversight of the effective implementation of the technology controls.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_a4de23dd-76d0-47f2-bd0f-093ed185c310">Oversight of risk management practices.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</specification>
<verification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_1c88f89a-dd33-451e-a8a3-1f38c7073a79" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_935dd2f5-2619-4de7-bc36-74c625dbec83">Determine that the responsibilities of management and board of directors in managing and overseeing information security risks are documented and communicated.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_c2961b2d-23b9-457e-8003-7c78b05a9be3">Inspect documents such as meeting minutes and committee charter to identify the participants involved in the meeting or committee, their respective job functions and the reporting relationship.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_71248367-171e-43b5-bc3f-c3e991783435">Determine whether the management and board of directors meet regularly, at an appropriate and monitored frequency.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_d0e66245-467c-4fe5-904f-fa58051b4d4e">Determine whether the information security function is headed by a Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) or similar function.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</verification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_2_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 2 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_d0fb0c26-61b1-427a-a66b-9b216be47eae"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/2</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/1</inherit><description><p id="_5ae8dc99-0354-446d-9e3b-de90bb9db11d">The requirements and audit procedures are the same as those in Level 1.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"/></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_3_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Level 3 requirements and audit procedures</title><requirement id="_a646a484-13de-4125-aefc-1ee1e256ebf9"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/3</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/2</inherit><description><p id="_6ddabd33-b5cc-4b71-97f1-0d89b67dd868">The requirements are the same as those in Level 2.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"><p id="_e0691ee7-f654-48f3-b3ac-2a4053db894c">The audit procedures are those in Level 1 and the following:</p>     
<ol id="_6ed16707-89b9-4346-9854-2398461a82fe" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_8fbdf633-a45a-41dc-b71c-2ac9ba0056cc">Verify risks have been reviewed, understood, and addressed (i.e. including a cost benefit analysis) by management and the board.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol></verification></requirement>   
